msgid "SIR"
msgstr "处长"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:4
#: 2064271cec3d42a8841bc12ee4bc3b32
msgid ""
"The SIR Model [1]_ assumes that infection spreads only through links between"
" neighboring nodes in a graph :math:`G=(V,E)`. Each node is in one of three "
"states: :math:`S`, :math:`I`, or :math:`R`. A susceptible node :math:`i` is "
"infected by its infected neighbors :math:`j \\in N(i)` with rate "
":math:`\\beta`, while infected nodes recover with rate :math:`\\gamma`:"
msgstr ""
"SIR模型 [1] 假设感染只通过相邻节点之间的连接在图:math:`G=(V,E)'中传播. 每个节点位于三个州之一:`S'、`I'或`R'。 "
"一个易发节点:math:`i'被其感染的邻居感染 :math:`j\\in "
"N(i)',比例:math:``\\beta',而受感染的节点恢复率:math:``\\gamma':"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:9
#: 7b0bde77f2df4840bb204962109daa63
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\frac{dS_i}{dt} &= -\\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dI_i}{dt} &= \\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j - \\gamma I_i, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dR_i}{dt} &= \\gamma I_i .\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"\\ frac{ dS i}{dt}\\\\\\\\\\ beta\\ sum\\j\\ in N(i)}S i I j,\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dI i}{dt}\\ beta\\ sum {j\\ in N(i)} S i I j -\\gamma I i,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dR i}{dt}\\\\\\gamma I i 。\n"
"结束{对齐}"

