#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:65
#: 07f34a3aa5a54f0292905e00c253325b
msgid ""
"Node states are represented by two Boolean indicator vectors :math:`h, r "
"\\in \\{0,1\\}^N`, where :math:`h_i=1` denotes ``infected``, :math:`r_i=1` "
"denotes ``recovered``, and :math:`(h_i,r_i)=(0,0)` denotes ``susceptible``. "
"The update of the system at step :math:`k` is decomposed into three stages:"
msgstr ""
"节点状态由两个布尔指标矢量表示:`h, r\\ in \\{0, 1\\}^N',其中:`h i=1'表示“感染',`r i=1'表示“恢复',`(h "
"i, r i)=(0)'表示“可接受”。 系统分三个阶段更新:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:70
#: d3e4740fd9204c43b662153ac0c86728
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:节点的`j':math:`i ' 传递日志概率贡献"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:72
#: 05a848a9009d413db3695b26bb075633
msgid "m_{ji}^{(k)} = h_j^{(k-1)} \\cdot \\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)}=h j^{(k-1)}\\cdot\\log(1-\\β)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:77
#: 3c1e3819db1a4a70beffdaaa644f2528
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its infection probability"
msgstr "节点: \" i \" 收集所有邻居的贡献: \" N(i) \" 计算感染概率"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:79
#: 5367fdb81fdf4b2db4841b972eff8c61
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr "m i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)} m {ji}^{(k)}\\右)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:84
#: ea10f44502c0435ea9c7329a07535dba
msgid ""
"The indicator variables are updated with independent uniform random "
"variables :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\sim "
"\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`"
msgstr ""
"指标变量以独立的统一随机变量更新 : math :`U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}}, U i^{\\ "
"mathrm{rec}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)'"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIR.rst:86
#: ae28048d0a9b469cbf9ca9979fcd1850
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"    h_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"    \\begin{cases}\n"
"            1, & \\text{if } (h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land r_i^{(k-1)}=0) \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} < m_i^{(k)}), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            0, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=1 \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\ge \\gamma), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            h_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise},\n"
"    \\end{cases} \\\\[6pt]\n"
"    r_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"    \\begin{cases}\n"
"            1, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=1 \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} < \\gamma), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            r_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise}.\n"
"    \\end{cases}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"h(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} (h i^{(k-1)}=0\\land r i^{(k-1)}=0)\\land (U i^{\\mathrm{inf}}} < m i^{(k)}),\\\\[4pt]\n"
"0, &\\ text{if} h i^{(k-1)}=1\\land (U i^{\\ mathrm{rec}}}\\ge\\gamma),\\\\[4pt]\n"
"h i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类},\n"
"\\ end{ cases}\\\\\\ [6pt]\n"
"r i^{(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} h i^{(k-1)}\\%1\\land(U i^{\\ mathrm{rec}}} <\\gamma),\\\\[4pt]\n"
"r i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类}.\n"
"结束{ cases}\n"
"结束{对齐}"

